---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-16 border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-950 text-slate-300">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 md:grid-cols-4 lg:px-8">
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <div class="font-heading text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">FlowHome</div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-6">Independent smart home buying guides, comparison tools, and deal tracking for US and Canada readers. We prioritize useful products, strong owner feedback, ecosystem compatibility, and clear long-term value.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-white">Explore</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/deals/" class="hover:text-white">Deals</a></li>
        <li><a href="/calculator/" class="hover:text-white">Savings Calculator</a></li>
        <li><a href="/quiz/" class="hover:text-white">Recommendation Quiz</a></li>
        <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="hover:text-white">RSS</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-bold text-white">Trust</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white">About FlowHome</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about/#affiliate-policy" class="hover:text-white">Affiliate policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="hover:text-white">Sitemap</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-slate-800 px-4 py-5 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">© {year} FlowHome. As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases.</div>
</footer>
